    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I had the same issue with <strong>OkHttpClient</strong> and <strong>HttpURLConnection</strong>.\nMy android emulator was configured to use proxy, but my proxy wasn't accepting connections.</p>\n\n<p>Doesn't mater if you use proxy or not if destination host refuses connection you will get that exception.</p>\n"
